description.text: This table contains information about happy hours at shops, including the shop's identifier, the month of the happy hour, and the number of staff in charge.

EventDetails.text: This class contains information about happy hours at shops. It includes the shop's identifier, the month of the happy hour, and the unique identifier for the happy hour event.

StaffMetrics.text: This class focuses on the number of staff members in charge during the happy hour.

HH_ID.text: Unique identifier for the happy hour event

Shop_ID.text: Identifier of the shop hosting the happy hour

Month.text: Month in which the happy hour takes place

Num_of_staff_in_charge.text: Number of staff members in charge during the happy hour

description.text: This table contains information about members, including their name, membership card details, age, time of purchase, level of membership, and address.

MemberDetails.text: This class contains detailed information about members, including their name, membership card details, age, time of purchase, level of membership, and address.

description.text: This table contains information about shops, including their address, number of staff, score, and opening year.

ShopDetails.text: This class contains information about shops, including their address, number of staff, score, and opening year.

Num_of_staff.text: Number of staff members working at the shop

Score.text: Score or rating of the shop

description.text: This table represents member participation in happy hour events, including the happy hour event identifier, member identifier, and total amount spent during the happy hour.

ParticipationDetails.text: This class represents member participation in happy hour events. It includes the happy hour event identifier, member identifier, and total amount spent during the happy hour.

SpendingMetrics.text: This class comprises metrics related to member spending during the happy hour.

HH_ID.text: Identifier of the happy hour event

Member_ID.text: Identifier of the member participating in the happy hour

Total_amount.text: Total amount spent by the member during the happy hour
